                </h3>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
                    Own your games forever. No online checks, no restrictions. Play anywhere, anytime.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="group p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-2xl bg-card border border-border hover:border-primary/50 transition-all duration-300 animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors">
                    <i class="fas fa-users w-7 h-7 text-primary"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-orbitron text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                    Vibrant Community
                </h3>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
                    Connect with millions of gamers. Share experiences, strategies, and make lasting friendships.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="group p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-2xl bg-card border border-border hover:border-primary/50 transition-all duration-300 animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors">
                    <i class="fas fa-calendar w-7 h-7 text-primary"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-orbitron text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                    Epic Events
                </h3>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
                    From tournaments to community nights, there's always something exciting happening.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="group p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-2xl bg-card border border-border hover:border-primary/50 transition-all duration-300 animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors">
                    <i class="fas fa-download w-7 h-7 text-primary"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-orbitron text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                    Instant Access
                </h3>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
                    Download and play immediately. No waiting, no queues, just pure gaming.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="group p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-2xl bg-card border border-border hover:border-primary/50 transition-all duration-300 animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors">
                    <i class="fas fa-bolt w-7 h-7 text-primary"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-orbitron text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                    Lightning Fast
                </h3>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
                    Optimized downloads and seamless updates. Get into the action faster than ever.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="group p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-2xl bg-card border border-border hover:border-primary/50 transition-all duration-300 animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors">
                    <i class="fas fa-trophy w-7 h-7 text-primary"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-orbitron text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                    Achievements
                </h3>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
                    Track your progress, unlock achievements, and showcase your gaming prowess.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Newsletter Section -->
<section class="py-20 lg:py-32 relative overflow-hidden hero-gradient">
    <!-- Background Elements -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 grid-pattern opacity-30"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-secondary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
            <!-- Badge -->
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-primary/10 border border-primary/30 mb-8">
                <i class="fas fa-sparkles w-4 h-4 text-primary"></i>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-primary">Stay Updated</span>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Heading -->
            <h2 class="font-orbitron text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
                <span class="text-foreground">Never Miss a</span>
                <br />
                <span class="text-gradient">Gaming Moment</span>
            </h2>
            
            <!-- Description -->
            <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
                Subscribe to our newsletter for exclusive deals, game releases, tournament updates, and community highlights.
            </p>
            
            <!-- Form -->
            <form class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 max-w-md mx-auto">
                <div class="relative flex-1">
                    <i class="fas fa-envelope absolute left-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-muted-foreground"></i>
                    <input type="email" placeholder="Enter your email" class="w-full pl-12 h-12 bg-background/50 border border-border backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:border-primary text-foreground placeholder-muted-foreground transition-colors" required />
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn-hero">
                    Subscribe
                </button>
            </form>
            
            <!-- Trust -->
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-6">
                Join 50,000+ gamers. No spam, unsubscribe anytime.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
{% endblock %}
